**/repos/*/
**/parts
**/sdist
**/secret
**/secrets
**/shrinkwrap.yaml
**/storybook-static
**/target
**/temp
**/tmp
**/tmpcharts
**/tsconfig.tsbuildinfo
**/nosetests.xml
**/pip-log.txt
**/yarn-metadata.json
**/yarn.lock
**/kuber/kuber
lab/styleguidist/styleguide/
docs/blog/public
