repos/**/*
src/dsp/widgets
var/**/*
var/srv/certs/*
var/srv/jupyterhub/*
github_issue_summarization/build/
**/github_issue_summarization/hp-tune/vendor
# Exclude Terraform
**/aws_credentials.tf
**/rds_credentials.tf
**/*.tfstate
**/*.tfstate.backup
**/terraform.tfstate*
**/aws.pem*
**/terraform.tfvars
**/*.tfstate*
# Excluse VIM
**/[._]*.s[a-v][a-z]
**/[._]*.sw[a-p]
**/[._]s[a-rt-v][a-z]
**/[._]ss[a-gi-z]
**/[._]sw[a-p]

# Include

!**/.*ignore
!**/.*rc
!**/.*rc.js
!**/.*config
!**/.datalayer
!**/.github
!**/.storybook
!**/.vscode
!.gitattributes
!.readthedocs.yml
!bin
!dist/README.md
!opt/README.md
!repos/README.md
!sbin/build
!sbin/clean
!sbin/install
!sbin/start
!sbin/start-80
!srv/**/README.md
!var/**/README.md

# Re-Exclude (if needed)
**/_book/*
**/_book/.*
